<h2>What GEO Scoring Measures</h2>
<p>GEO scoring quantifies how likely AI search engines are to discover, understand, and cite your content. It is not one metric. It is a framework of metrics that cover different dimensions of AI visibility.</p>
<p>Think of it this way. SEO scoring tells you how well your page performs in traditional Google search. <a href="/blog/what-is-geo/">GEO scoring</a> tells you how well your page performs in AI-generated responses.</p>
<h3>The Core Question GEO Scoring Answers</h3>
<p>Can AI systems find your content, parse its structure, extract relevant facts, and cite it accurately when answering user queries?</p>
<p>A high GEO score means yes across all 4 dimensions. A low score means your content has gaps in at least one of them.</p>
