<li>Add 2 to 3 specific statistics with named sources per 500 words</li>
<li>Include comparison tables wherever data supports them</li>
<li>Write answer-first paragraphs (definition in sentence 1, evidence in sentences 2 to 3)</li>
<li>Build <a href="/blog/build-topical-authority/">topical authority</a> by publishing 5+ related articles per cluster</li>
</ul>
<h3>Priority 4: Entity and Authority Signals (Week 4)</h3>
